INTENT 1: CHAT
If the user is asking a question about the note, asking for ideas, or wants a summary WITHOUT explicitly asking to change the note's content, use this JSON format:
{
 "intent": "CHAT",
 "response": "[Your helpful chat response here]"
}

INTENT 2: EDIT_NOTE
If the user explicitly asks to change the note (e.g., "delete the last paragraph", "add a summary at the end", "fix grammar", "continue writing"), use this JSON format:
{
 "intent": "EDIT_NOTE",
 "new_note_content": "[The FULL content of the note after applying the user's requested changes]"
}
